            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratores</ex></expan> Caesares <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Aurelius Antoninus et <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Aurelius <del rend="erasure">Commodus <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustus</ex></expan></del> Germanici <lb n="3"/>Sarmatici fortissimi amphitheatrum <lb n="4"/>vetustate corruptum a solo resti<lb break="no" n="5"/>tuerunt per <expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortem</ex></expan> VI <expan><abbr>Commag</abbr><ex>enorum</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex>ulo</ex></expan> Iulio Pompilio Pisone Laevillo <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ato</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetore</ex></expan> curante Aelio Sereno <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ecto</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: A. Iulius Pompilius Piso war um 176/177 n. Chr. kaiserlicher Legat in Numidien.</p>
            </div>
